1.	Download Image form: https://hub.docker.com/

Choose needed version, copy command.
Example, I choose the tensorflow 2.1: docker pull tensorflow/tensorflow:2.1.2-gpu
List image:

  docker images
2.	Create container:
$docker run --gpus all --shm-size 128gb --name ($container_name) -it (images_id) 
 
3.	Install some package
apt update
apt install ffmpeg

apt install python3-opencv
apt-get install wget
apt install vim
apt-get install unzip
apt-get update 
apt-get install ffmpeg libsm6 libxext6  -y
pip install matplotlib 
pip install ipython

